  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our new Top Seller game:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/513990/extras/6181323adc77768af1c33c896748ba92.avif?t=1649688567\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>In a faraway land, Charming Princess Leya governed her lovely people in the Happy Empire. One day, her thirst for knowledge and discovery of new lands inspired her to venture on a long journey. During her absence, an evil wizard named Moramor advanced and captured the Happy Empire.<br><br>Help the princess overcome difficulties, banish the evil wizard and restore the empire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/513990/extras/b7bbb40779c9cd5413f8710a5ec7759d.avif?t=1649688567\" width=600 height=469 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More About the Game:</h2><br>- Detailed and dazzling graphics<br>- Visit three different worlds<br>- Help the story end happily<br>- Manage resources and test your abilities!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/513990/extras/6181323adc77768af1c33c896748ba92.avif?t=1649688567\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>In a faraway land, Charming Princess Leya governed her lovely people in the Happy Empire. One day, her thirst for knowledge and discovery of new lands inspired her to venture on a long journey. During her absence, an evil wizard named Moramor advanced and captured the Happy Empire.<br><br>Help the princess overcome difficulties, banish the evil wizard and restore the empire!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/513990/extras/b7bbb40779c9cd5413f8710a5ec7759d.avif?t=1649688567\" width=600 height=469 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More About the Game:</h2><br>- Detailed and dazzling graphics<br>- Visit three different worlds<br>- Help the story end happily<br>- Manage resources and test your abilities!",
